{"tid":1366441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【七警案】其中2警上訴得直 其餘5人獲減刑即時入獄","createTime":"2019-07-26T03:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T04:02:46.000Z","uid":218975,"like":2,"dislike":188,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"67cad50d5f65ffca97b7bfd7e2888e63a88b1d08","tid":1366441,"uid":218975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:11:43.000Z","msg":"七名警員5年前在金鐘添馬公園暗角毆打前公民黨成員曾健超一案，前年在區域法院被裁定罪名成立，7警各被判囚2年，但七警不服定罪及刑期而提出上訴，上訴庭把案押後至今近7個月，將於今早頒下裁決。<br />\n<br />\n觀塘反黑組警員劉興沛及觀塘反黑組警員黃偉豪上訴得直，而有組織及三合會調查科總督察黃祖成<br />\n、觀塘反黑組高級督察劉卓毅、觀塘反黑組警長白榮斌、東九龍總區偵緝警員陳少丹及九龍城區刑事偵緝警員關嘉豪上訴被駁回，但獲減刑。<br />\n<br />\n兩獲撤銷定罪刑期的警員聞判後鬆了一口氣。"},{"pid":"15cb49a10f640a26eb5e5d6a551ded2ed61a734c","tid":1366441,"uid":218975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:12:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"003339b58c66b4e65132c8d7ea38b27f3ae9abc8","tid":1366441,"uid":218975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:12:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3da9d2bc6e3047f2dcce64bf906b6253750046ed","tid":1366441,"uid":218975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:14:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5ddf6865cc8fb5175e2bdff6630e6031ba1d25f1","tid":1366441,"uid":10757,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:14:27.000Z","msg":"我屌你老母 相信司法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"176e2d8ba5b55f111450463c56df8844467b9a00","tid":1366441,"uid":42108,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:14:37.000Z","msg":"得直嘅個兩個一定要搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508226de74a91507b67b74f99ba043b1c1308fd7","tid":1366441,"uid":4493,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T03:15:02.000Z","msg":"其實預咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n星期六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" clas